{"tid":2441126,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"維園流水式集會案　黎智英等人控罪被裁定表證成立","createTime":"2021-03-10T12:35:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T12:40:43.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ec20881b0ea1d28eb9c61fbea29eea1503c545f9","tid":2441126,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T12:35:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579807-20210310.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579807-20210310.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPpsm%2Bn8Fwo%2F6aJUx9arcu0Q%3D&h=971bcf00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579807-20210310.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=be950e73\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579807-20210310.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒集團創辦人黎智英等9名民主派人士，涉嫌參與前年8月18日維園「流水式集會」，被控組織及參與未經批准集結，案件在西九龍法院大樓續審，控方證人作供全部完畢，法官裁定所有控罪表面證據成立。案件押後至明天，辯方會決定會否傳召證人。<br />\n<br />\n案件由區域法院法官胡雅文審理，案中2名被告區諾軒及梁耀忠早前已認罪，其餘7人否認控罪，包括黎智英、李柱銘、何俊仁、李卓人、梁國雄、吳靄儀及何秀蘭。"},{"pid":"477357089430f07b3766f2b721ed86fce25e0b16","tid":2441126,"uid":45975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T12:36:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d023723f52e48a119a3c36e79300021b09d17161","tid":2441126,"uid":105691,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T12:40:43.000Z","msg":"好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n死黑警 <br />\n應承我 大家要移民抗爭<br />\n我真係好撚鐘意香港<br />\n不自由 毋寧死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}